{"tid":555713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[女權撚]兩男指控非禮性騷擾 #MeToo推手女議員：唔記得喎","createTime":"2018-02-09T17:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T16:43:41.000Z","uid":132859,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f3e24dbe646e961385097aa881fbaa91f9e0de","tid":555713,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"美國加州民主黨議員、反性侵反性騷擾運動「＃MeToo」舵手加西亞（Cristina Garcia），被兩名男士指控非禮及性騷擾，她表示對事件「記不起」。<br />\n<br />\n40歲的加西亞是女性議員黨團（Legislative Women's Caucus）團長，也是國內反性騷擾運動的領導人物，更獲《時代》雜誌稱為性騷擾議題的「打破沉默者」。Politico周四報道，兩名男士指控加西亞非禮及性騷擾，其中一人是曾為民主黨議員卡爾德龍（Ian Calderon）打工的菲耶羅（Daniel Fierro）。<br />\n<br />\n事發在2014年，加西亞在一場壘球賽後，在球員席撫摸當時只有25歲的菲耶羅的背部和臀部，又嘗試觸碰他的下體。卡爾德龍的傳訊經理施莉妮安（Lerna Shirinian）表示，菲耶羅在事發後馬上將事件告訴她，她說：「他感到震驚、我感到震驚&hellip;&hellip;但那時文化非常不同。」如今開傳訊公司的菲耶羅，在上月將事件告知卡爾德龍，卡爾德龍向議會領袖匯報事件。<br />\n<br />\n事發在2014年，加西亞在一場壘球賽後，在球員席撫摸當時只有25歲的菲耶羅的背部和臀部，又嘗試觸碰他的下體。卡爾德龍的傳訊經理施莉妮安（Lerna Shirinian）表示，菲耶羅在事發後馬上將事件告訴她，她說：「他感到震驚、我感到震驚&hellip;&hellip;但那時文化非常不同。」如今開傳訊公司的菲耶羅，在上月將事件告知卡爾德龍，卡爾德龍向議會領袖匯報事件。<br />\n<br />\n另一名不願透露姓名的說客，亦指加西亞在去年一個籌款活動上，對他作出粗魯的性言論，並嘗試抓他的下體。菲耶羅與這位說客都指，加西亞在事發時似乎喝醉了。<br />\n<br />\n加西亞一直對捲入性騷擾指控的男議員口誅筆伐不遺餘力，又曾說酒精也不能做不恰當行為的藉口。加西亞曾道：「我想公眾期望我們對自己有更高的標準。」<br />\n<br />\n今次被指非禮及性騷擾多位男士，加西亞發聲明回應：「我一丁點兒也記不起，自己曾做過不恰當的行為。這些行為，是與我的價值觀不一致的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180209&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57810797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180209%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57810797&d=aIZMRU5ExBvnv7AKmHg6R54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e97637e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180209%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57810797&h=4085564d\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180209&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57810797</a><br />\nNo means no<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIt's time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEnd matriarchy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb3eec7da073fab5537da0b21501488b63c1d1e","tid":555713,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f79507ba2da59f5f84dbb23092961b296b8135","tid":555713,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">@ 柴田ミチコ<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0a0c745f8ed9093b584c76c4389379c35761a835","tid":555713,"uid":48796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"已經估到佢乜嘢樣了，講還講唔好貼相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394e697ffc3540a85a3545c23528cb22c6bce3e5","tid":555713,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T18:14:53.000Z","msg":"「他感到震驚、我感到震驚&hellip;&hellip;但那時文化非常不同。」<br />\n<br />\n好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有班男人俾人話幾十年前性騷擾其他人，當事人話個陣文化唔同就俾人屌<br />\n話無論咩時代都好，都係唔岩，逼到人認罪為止<br />\n依家metoo推手搞人，為左cover佢就變左「那時文化非常不同」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來性騷擾指控都有得咁分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以為假新聞，原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLerna Shirinian, the communications director for Calderon, said &ldquo;I remember it very clearly, he told me as soon as it happened..he was in shock, I was in shock &mdash; but the culture was very different back then,&rsquo;&rsquo; Shirinian said, noting the admission was in confidence and she had to respect her friend&rsquo;s decision not to report it.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/story/2018/02/08/cristina-garcia-california-metoo-398985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2Fcristina-garcia-california-metoo-398985&d=aIZMRU5ExBvnv7AKmHg6R54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=81e350c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/story/2018/02/08/cristina-garcia-california-metoo-398985</a>"},{"pid":"22521fd5152acfe43833703d689931e5a52f82f2","tid":555713,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93f79507ba2da59f5f84dbb23092961b296b8135","tid":555713,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">@ 柴田ミチコ<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T18:16:51.000Z","msg":"柴田妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0784fcc4f42003f381869d960f1d16dfbc120164","tid":555713,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雙重標準"},{"pid":"0828e25f8b37092bd4cf65ef74494bc9d4d592f9","tid":555713,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"男人條j俾人任摸任揸no one cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cbb453bfc184f6f6f12a6a1651cbf42259f47d","tid":555713,"uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T19:03:09.000Z","msg":"呢班女人將法治催毀, 男人唔出聲有鳩用.<br />\n女權本質就係要取代父權, 非平等"},{"pid":"4f9f39ebac2c59ad64c77023980b11a392c390a1","tid":555713,"uid":12565,"like":13,"dislike":0,"sc